File: A general view of the headquarters of Eskom. AFP/Gianluigi Guercia  JOHANNESBURG - Stage 4 blackouts will be implemented from 4pm on Thursday until 5am on Friday. Thereafter, Stage 3 power cuts will then be in place until Sunday morning. Eskom says this is due to delays in the return to service of 7 generating units. Read the statement from Eskom below. #PowerAlert1
